{
  "video_id": "U-USPqbjmzo",
  "title": "Penal Code 459 -- Burglary",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4280.0,
      "end_time": 8690.0,
      "text": "-In Penal Code Section 459, California law defines"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8690.0,
      "end_time": 12829.0,
      "text": "burglary as entering a structure with the intent to"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12830.0,
      "end_time": 16940.0,
      "text": "commit either a theft or some felony inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16940.0,
      "end_time": 21200.0,
      "text": "Now a lot of people confuse burglary with robbery and"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21200.0,
      "end_time": 24480.0,
      "text": "theft, and they&#39;re actually three very different concepts."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24480.0,
      "end_time": 28400.0,
      "text": "Robbery is when you use violence or threats of"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28400.0,
      "end_time": 30770.0,
      "text": "violence to take something from somebody&#39;s immediate"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30770.0,
      "end_time": 34510.0,
      "text": "presence, like a mugging or a hold-up."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34510.0,
      "end_time": 38230.0,
      "text": "Theft is basically anytime you steal something of value."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38230.0,
      "end_time": 41550.0,
      "text": "Whereas burglary, on the other hand, is when you enter a"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41550.0,
      "end_time": 42360.0,
      "text": "structure--"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42360.0,
      "end_time": 44700.0,
      "text": "and that could be a house, it could be a business, it could"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44700.0,
      "end_time": 45740.0,
      "text": "be a factory--"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 45740.0,
      "end_time": 48930.0,
      "text": "but entering a structure or a building with the intent to"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48930.0,
      "end_time": 51630.0,
      "text": "commit theft or a felony inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51630.0,
      "end_time": 55200.0,
      "text": "-For example, a burglary, under California Penal Code"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55200.0,
      "end_time": 60000.0,
      "text": "459, can be a situation where somebody breaks into a home"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60000.0,
      "end_time": 63670.0,
      "text": "with the intent to steal clothing items, jewelry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63670.0,
      "end_time": 65220.0,
      "text": "whatever else might be present."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65220.0,
      "end_time": 68570.0,
      "text": "Another example of burglary can be going into a bank to"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68570.0,
      "end_time": 70809.0,
      "text": "cash a check that you know is bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70810.0,
      "end_time": 74240.0,
      "text": "A different example of burglary can be a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74240.0,
      "end_time": 77350.0,
      "text": "where a person goes to a child-care facility with the"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 77350.0,
      "end_time": 80700.0,
      "text": "intent to commit assault on a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80700.0,
      "end_time": 83720.0,
      "text": "Now that isn&#39;t theft, but you are going there with the"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83720.0,
      "end_time": 87690.0,
      "text": "intent to commit a felony, and therefore, it is burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87690.0,
      "end_time": 91390.0,
      "text": "-Under California Penal Code 459, merely entering a"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91390.0,
      "end_time": 95300.0,
      "text": "structure with the intent to commit a theft, or any felony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95300.0,
      "end_time": 98900.0,
      "text": "once you&#39;re inside constitutes a burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98900.0,
      "end_time": 100840.0,
      "text": "So really, entry is the crux of the crime here."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100840.0,
      "end_time": 104560.0,
      "text": "For example, say you enter your neighbor&#39;s home with the"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104560.0,
      "end_time": 107250.0,
      "text": "intent to steal his computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107250.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "And when you&#39;re inside his home, you realize that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 111390.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t find the computer and it&#39;s not there."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111390.0,
      "end_time": 114330.0,
      "text": "That still constitutes the burglary, because you entered"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114330.0,
      "end_time": 116870.0,
      "text": "the home to commit a theft of his computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116870.0,
      "end_time": 118400.0,
      "text": "once you were inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118400.0,
      "end_time": 120690.0,
      "text": "So it doesn&#39;t even matter that you didn&#39;t actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120690.0,
      "end_time": 122240.0,
      "text": "complete the crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122240.0,
      "end_time": 124580.0,
      "text": "Thus, entry is really the most important"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124580.0,
      "end_time": 126500.0,
      "text": "element of a burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126500.0,
      "end_time": 130269.0,
      "text": "-There&#39;s also a lot of confusion between burglary and"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130270.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132990.0,
      "text": "the idea of breaking and entering."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132990.0,
      "end_time": 137500.0,
      "text": "The fact is that in California law, breaking and entering is"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 137500.0,
      "end_time": 139300.0,
      "text": "not an element of burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139300.0,
      "end_time": 142910.0,
      "text": "What that means, essentially, is that you could be convicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142910.0,
      "end_time": 146340.0,
      "text": "of burglary even if there was no forced entry."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 146340.0,
      "end_time": 149530.0,
      "text": "And to give you an example, suppose I&#39;m walking down the"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149530.0,
      "end_time": 152800.0,
      "text": "street, and I look inside a house."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152800.0,
      "end_time": 156930.0,
      "text": "And the front door is wide open, and inside the door is a"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156930.0,
      "end_time": 159150.0,
      "text": "bicycle that I want to steal."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 159150.0,
      "end_time": 162460.0,
      "text": "So I walk through that open front door, take the"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 162460.0,
      "end_time": 164250.0,
      "text": "bicycle, and leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 164250.0,
      "end_time": 167550.0,
      "text": "Now in that situation, there was no forced entry."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167550.0,
      "end_time": 168950.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t even have to open the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 168950.0,
      "end_time": 172790.0,
      "text": "I mean, even though the door was wide open, the mere fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 172800.0,
      "end_time": 175320.0,
      "text": "that I entered the house or the structure with the intent"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 175320.0,
      "end_time": 178185.0,
      "text": "to commit a theft inside is enough to make it a burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 182470.0,
      "end_time": 186640.0,
      "text": "-Under California Penal Code 459, first degree residential"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 186640.0,
      "end_time": 189500.0,
      "text": "burglary is treated much more seriously"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 189500.0,
      "end_time": 190910.0,
      "text": "than commercial burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 190910.0,
      "end_time": 193190.0,
      "text": "We treat our homes as our castle, and therefore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 193190.0,
      "end_time": 196790.0,
      "text": "residential burglary has more harsh penalties."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 196790.0,
      "end_time": 198290.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s always a felony."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198290.0,
      "end_time": 199929.0,
      "text": "It is always a strike."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199930.0,
      "end_time": 203800.0,
      "text": "A person can face up to six years&#39; incarceration as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203800.0,
      "end_time": 205880.0,
      "text": "as a $10,000 fine for this charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205880.0,
      "end_time": 210570.0,
      "text": "A person will be liable for entry into any residence."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210570.0,
      "end_time": 213489.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have to be a house in the traditional sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213490.0,
      "end_time": 216590.0,
      "text": "It could be a hotel where a person is staying."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216590.0,
      "end_time": 219840.0,
      "text": "Here in California, there was even a case where a person was"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219840.0,
      "end_time": 223120.0,
      "text": "liable for residential burglary for breaking into a"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 223120.0,
      "end_time": 225580.0,
      "text": "tent where a homeless person was living."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225580.0,
      "end_time": 226680.0,
      "text": "It was a structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226680.0,
      "end_time": 227885.0,
      "text": "It had four sides."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227885.0,
      "end_time": 229269.0,
      "text": "It had a roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 229270.0,
      "end_time": 231180.0,
      "text": "A person was living in there."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231180.0,
      "end_time": 233200.0,
      "text": "That makes it residential burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 233200.0,
      "end_time": 237290.0,
      "text": "-By contrast, California Penal Code 459 treats second degree"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 237290.0,
      "end_time": 240269.0,
      "text": "burglary, otherwise known as commercial burglary, a little"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 240270.0,
      "end_time": 241410.0,
      "text": "less severely."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241410.0,
      "end_time": 244540.0,
      "text": "Commercial burglary is where you enter a business, or a"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 244540.0,
      "end_time": 249300.0,
      "text": "factory, or someplace where you know no one resides."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 249300.0,
      "end_time": 251490.0,
      "text": "Here in California, commercial burglary is what&#39;s called a"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 251490.0,
      "end_time": 254830.0,
      "text": "\"wobbler,\" which means the prosecutor can choose to file"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 254830.0,
      "end_time": 257850.0,
      "text": "it as either a felony or a misdemeanor, depending on the"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257850.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259610.00000000003,
      "text": "circumstances of the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259610.0,
      "end_time": 261890.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re convicted of felony commercial burglary in"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 261890.0,
      "end_time": 265380.0,
      "text": "California, you face up to three years in state prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 265380.0,
      "end_time": 268159.0,
      "text": "However, if you&#39;re convicted of a misdemeanor commercial"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268160.0,
      "end_time": 271310.0,
      "text": "burglary, you only face up to one year in county jail."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275100.0,
      "end_time": 277760.0,
      "text": "-Burglary is one of those crimes that can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 277760.0,
      "end_time": 281440.0,
      "text": "surprisingly difficult for the prosecutor to prove in court."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 281440.0,
      "end_time": 286500.0,
      "text": "And in fact, lots of innocent people get wrongfully accused"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 286500.0,
      "end_time": 287680.0,
      "text": "of burglary, and sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 287680.0,
      "end_time": 290100.0,
      "text": "tragically, wrongfully convicted."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290100.0,
      "end_time": 293400.0,
      "text": "The good news is that here at Shouse Law Group, we&#39;ve had a"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293400.0,
      "end_time": 297150.0,
      "text": "great record of success over the years in fighting burglary"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 297150.0,
      "end_time": 300190.0,
      "text": "charges and helping our clients to get those charges"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 300190.0,
      "end_time": 302190.0,
      "text": "reduced or even dismissed."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 302190.0,
      "end_time": 305370.0,
      "text": "-One common defense to burglary is what we call"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 305370.0,
      "end_time": 309870.0,
      "text": "\"after-acquired intent.\" What that means is that you did not"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 309870.0,
      "end_time": 313300.0,
      "text": "have any intent to commit a theft, you did not have any"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 313300.0,
      "end_time": 316609.0,
      "text": "intent to commit a felony, until after you were already"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 316610.0,
      "end_time": 318700.0,
      "text": "inside the structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 318700.0,
      "end_time": 320890.0,
      "text": "For example, you walk into Bloomingdale&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 320890.0,
      "end_time": 323110.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re just going to do some shopping."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 323110.0,
      "end_time": 325910.0,
      "text": "But you find this outfit, and you fall in love with this"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 325910.0,
      "end_time": 329900.0,
      "text": "outfit, but you can&#39;t afford that outfit."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 329900.0,
      "end_time": 331919.0,
      "text": "And for some reason, spontaneously, you"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 331920.0,
      "end_time": 333320.0,
      "text": "decide to steal it."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 333320.0,
      "end_time": 335490.0,
      "text": "So you walk out of the store with that"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 335490.0,
      "end_time": 337660.0,
      "text": "outfit and without paying."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 337660.0,
      "end_time": 340700.0,
      "text": "Sure you&#39;re likely liable for a theft, but"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 340700.0,
      "end_time": 341790.0,
      "text": "that is not a burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 341790.0,
      "end_time": 345290.0,
      "text": "And it is not a burglary because when you walked into"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 345290.0,
      "end_time": 349480.0,
      "text": "the store, you did not yet have any intent to steal."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 349480.0,
      "end_time": 351740.0,
      "text": "-Another common defense in a burglary case is"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 351740.0,
      "end_time": 353570.0,
      "text": "misidentification."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 353570.0,
      "end_time": 357920.0,
      "text": "Mistaken eyewitness ID is the number-one reason for wrongful"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 357920.0,
      "end_time": 361000.0,
      "text": "arrests and convictions across the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 361000.0,
      "end_time": 364390.0,
      "text": "And it certainly results in a lot of innocent people getting"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 364390.0,
      "end_time": 365950.0,
      "text": "arrested for burglary."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 365950.0,
      "end_time": 368479.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very common that a burglary occurs in the"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 368480.0,
      "end_time": 372610.0,
      "text": "vicinity, and you just happen to match the description that"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 372610.0,
      "end_time": 376400.0,
      "text": "an eyewitness gives to the police, and you&#39;re arrested."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 376400.0,
      "end_time": 380340.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s a defense attorney&#39;s job to show the prosecutor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 380340.0,
      "end_time": 384690.0,
      "text": "the court, and even possibly a jury that this is a case of"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 384690.0,
      "end_time": 388900.0,
      "text": "mistaken identification and that you were not actually the"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 388900.0,
      "end_time": 389479.0,
      "text": "perpetrator of this crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 389480.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "-Another common defense to a burglary charge in California"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 396500.0,
      "text": "is what we call being merely present."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 396500.0,
      "end_time": 399160.0,
      "text": "What that means is you may be hanging out with some people"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 399160.0,
      "end_time": 400650.0,
      "text": "who decide to commit a burglary"
    },
